          "answer": "【要点归纳】文体与格式：本题要求写一封正式投诉邮件，需包含完整的书信格式（称呼、正文、结尾敬语、署名）。语气与态度：收信对象为客服人员，语气应礼貌得体，既要清晰表达不满，也要尊重对方工作，避免过于生硬或情绪化。内容要点：简要说明购买情况（产品名称、购买时间与渠道）；具体描述产品存在的问题；明确提出解决方案（如换货、维修或退款）；结尾表达感谢或期望，并留下联系方式。【范文参考】Dear Sir or Madam,I am writing to express my dissatisfaction with an electronic dictionary (Model P90o) that I purchased from your online store the day before yesterday. Unfortunately, it has not been functioning properly. The device frequently shuts down on its own, which severely affects its usability.I would appreciate it if you could arrange for a replacement or repair as per the warranty policy. If neither option is feasible, I would request a full refund.Thank you for your attention to this matter. Please feel free to contact me at 12345678 if further details are needed.Yours faithfully,Zhang Wei【写作储备】常见电子词典问题表达：short battery life 电池续航短unable to update 无法更新系统stuck key / keys difficult to press 按键卡顿/难以按下broken screen 屏幕破损frequent application crash 程序频繁闪退投诉信常用句型：开头表达不满：I wish to complain about…I am writing to express my dissatisfaction with…I must bring to your attention a problem with…描述问题：It is frustrating to find that…I am disappointed because the product does not work as expected.The device malfunctions frequently, which is highly inconvenient.提出诉求：I would appreciate it if you could replace/repair/refund…I request that you resolve this issue at your earliest convenience.结尾礼貌提醒：I trust you will give this matter your prompt attention.I look forward to your reply and a satisfactory solution.改写说明：结构和格式标准化：将原文要点、范文、写作储备等内容按标准书信解析结构分段整理，条理更清晰，便于阅读和查找。表达和逻辑优化：对原文解析和例句进行语言润色，调整部分表述，使逻辑更顺畅、语气更正式。内容补充与细化：在常用表达和问题类型部分适当补充和细化内容，增强实用性和指导性。如果您需要其他风格或进一步调整，请随时告知，我会为您优化。",
