          "body": "Directions\nSuppose your university is going to host a summer camp for high school students. Write a notice to\nbriefly introduce the camp activities, andcall for volunteers.\nYou should write about 100 words on the ANSWER SHEET.\nDo not use your name or the name of your university.\nDo not write your address. (10 points)",
          "options": [],
          "answer": "【要点归纳】文体类型：告示。写作时需确保格式正确、完整。核心目的：招募志愿者。内容应具有吸引力与号召力。主要内容：简要介绍夏令营活动内容，突出其意义与特色；说明志愿者的职责与要求；提供报名或联系方式。【范文参考】Recruitment AnnouncementWe are looking for volunteers for the upcoming summer camp for high school students. The camp aims to enhance participants’ academic abilities and develop their teamwork and practical skills through various activities such as reading salons and entrepreneurship competitions.Volunteers will assist in organizing activities and managing daily operations. Ideal candidates should be patient, proactive, warm-hearted, and responsible. Relevant experience is preferred. Interested students please contact us at studentsunion@abcuniversity.edu.cn or call 12345678.Students’ Union【写作储备】一、夏令营的意义make new friends 结交新朋友learn new skills 学习新技能discover and grow 发现与成长expand one’s horizon 开阔视野learn to be independent 学会独立二、招募类表达句型开头引入，说明目的We are seeking volunteers to work with us in…We plan to recruit… for…Since its establishment in…, the program has become a leading activity in…This role offers a challenging, stimulating and rewarding experience.说明要求与条件To be considered for…, you will ideally possess…Candidates for this position should have…Volunteers are expected to…提供联系方式If you are interested, please send your resume to…For further information, feel free to contact…",
