          "reference": "【题目解析】信件类型：这是一封回复朋友祝贺并给予建议的回信，属于半正式书信。语气要求：语气应热情友好，体现感谢之意与分享精神。内容要点：感谢对方的祝贺；针对翻译学习提出具体建议（2–3条）；表达进一步交流的意愿并期待回复。格式规范：需包含称呼、正文、结尾敬语及署名，注意字数控制在100词左右。【参考范文】Dear Jack,Thank you so much for your warm congratulations on my translation contest success.As for advice, I believe the key lies in consistent practice and extensive reading. Try to engage with diverse texts—both Chinese and English—to enhance your sense of language. Also, learning about the cultures behind the languages can help you grasp nuanced meanings. Most importantly, keep practicing and stay curious.I hope these suggestions help. Feel free to ask me more—I’m always happy to discuss!Looking forward to your reply.Yours sincerely,Li Ming【写作储备】▌开头常用句式：I’m writing to express my sincere thanks for your congratulations.Thank you for your kind words regarding my achievement.▌提出建议常用表达：You asked for my advice on…, so I’d like to suggest that…It might be helpful to…I strongly recommend that you…Another useful tip is to…▌结尾常用语句：I hope you find my suggestions practical.I’m more than willing to talk more if you need.Feel free to reach out anytime for further discussion.改写说明：结构和条理优化：将原有内容拆分为解析、范文、句式积累三大板块，采用分级标题和条目化表达，使层次更清晰、逻辑更顺畅。表达精炼与规范：对原有冗余或口语化语句进行精简，统一术语和表达风格，提升解析和范文的专业性和正式度。格式标准化：整体采用更正式、易读的文档格式，合理运用标题、分段和列表，突出各板块重点。如果您需要其他风格或针对特定环节的改写，我可以继续为您调整内容。",
