          "body": "Directions\nSuppose you are planning a campus food festival, write an email to international students in your university to\nintroduce the food festivalinvite them to participate\nYou should write about 100 words on ANSWER SHEET. (10 points)\nDo not use your own name. Use “Li Ming” instead.",
          "options": [],
          "answer": "解析一、要点归纳格式：书信体（邀请信）。语域：面向国际学生，语言应亲切、自然，避免过于正式刻板。内容要点：介绍美食节的基本信息（时间、地点、特色等）。说明活动的具体安排与亮点（如特色菜肴、互动环节）。明确发出邀请，并阐述活动的意义。二、行文思路第一段：开门见山，点明活动（美食节），并交代核心信息（时间、地点），同时发出诚挚邀请。第二段：具体介绍活动内容，包括提供的特色美食以及鼓励学生参与的互动环节（如亲手烹饪），描绘活动现场氛围。第三段：总结活动价值，强化邀请，表达期待。三、范文分析范文：Dear international students,There will be a multicultural food festival at the Main Dining Hall from 10 a.m. to 3 p.m. on May 27th. You are cordially invited to this occasion.The event features a variety of local specialties, ranging from traditional homely delicacies to popular street snacks, all elaborately prepared by our catering staff. If interested, you are also encouraged to cook your hometown dishes in groups with the ingredients provided on site. This will definitely be a highlight of the event. After preparation, all participants can move along the booths, sampling these delicious foods with cheerful music.Don’t miss this golden opportunity to get a taste of different cultures and experience more joy in life! We keenly look forward to your participation.Yours sincerely, Li Ming四、核心表达储备开篇与邀请：You are cordially invited to… (诚挚邀请您参加……)We would be delighted if you could join us for… (如若您能参加……，我们将不胜欣喜。)On behalf of…, I invite you to attend… (我谨代表……，邀请您出席……)介绍活动：The event features… (本次活动特色是……)ranging from… to… (从……到……种类繁多)Participants will have the opportunity to… (参与者将有机会……)This event is designed to… (本次活动旨在……)结尾与呼吁：Don’t miss this golden opportunity to… (切勿错过这个……的良机！)We keenly look forward to your participation. (我们热切期待您的参与。)Your presence would be greatly appreciated. (我们将非常感谢您的莅临。)",
